      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MEPUNGA FLYER (7) has a fair record and proved too classy last time to win by 5 lengths at this track in a handy 25.64 beating Paw Fable. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Expected to measure up again. PAW OTIS (1) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Was out of placings last time (30.27) at The Meadows in a Grade 4/5, finishing fourth and beaten 4 lengths. Can feature in the finish. PAW HAZELTON (2) is worth forgiving for his last effort when fourth (26.03) at this track over 460m. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. MINER MICK (4) was well fancied last time on the strength of a win two back but could only manage fourth (30.03) at Sandown. Comes out of a solid form race last start.",
